===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# [[facial|Facial]] [[hair]] on the [[chin]], [[cheeks]] and [[jaw]].
# The cluster of small [[feather]]s at the base of the [[beak]] in some [[bird]]s.
# The [[appendage]]s to the jaw in some [[cetacean]]s, and to the mouth or jaws of some [[fish]]es.
# The [[byssus]] of certain [[shellfish]].
# The [[gill]]s of some [[bivalve]]s, such as the [[oyster]].
# In insects, the hairs of the [[labial]] [[palpus|palpi]] of moths and butterflies.
# {{lb|en|botany}} Long or stiff hairs on a plant; the [[awn]].
#: ''the '''beard''' of grain''
# A [[barb]] or sharp point of an arrow or other instrument, projecting backward to prevent the head from being easily drawn out.
# That part of the [[underside]] of a [[horse]]'s lower jaw which is above the chin, and bears the [[curb]] of a [[bridle]].
# {{lb|en|printing|dated}} That part of a [[type]] which is between the [[shoulder]] of the [[shank]] and the [[face]].
# {{lb|en|LGBT|slang}} A fake customer or companion, especially a woman who accompanies a [[gay]] male in order to give the impression that he is [[heterosexual]].

